<h2 id="sample-output">Sample output</h2>

<p>For indicating sample output from a program use the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;samp&gt;</code> tag.</p>

<div class="bd-example-wrapper">
    <ul class="nav nav-tabs" role="tablist">
        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
            <a class="nav-link active" data-toggle="tab" href="#result-85" role="tab" aria-controls="result-85" aria-selected="true">Result</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
            <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="tab" href="#html-85" role="tab" aria-controls="html-85" aria-selected="false">HTML Code</a>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="tab-content" id="examplte-tab-content-85">
        <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="result-85" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="result-85"><div class="bd-example">
<samp>This text is meant to be treated as sample output from a computer program.</samp>
</div></div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="html-85" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="html-85">
<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span class="nt">&lt;samp&gt;</span>This text is meant to be treated as sample output from a computer program.<span class="nt">&lt;/samp&gt;</span></code></pre></figure>
